text: All bags I bought here broke in few months time. I paid SGD 150+ per bag. I have ever bought other brands at lower prices, but the quality is much better. This is a big rip off, considering guess is such an old reputable brand. They even name themselves a designer brand.

I did went to Guess shop at Bugis... The Chinese salesgirl over there was so proud n unfriendly.. as if she worked at one of damn famous and branded SHOP like L.V SHOP. NO NEED TO LOOK DOWN OF PEOPLE WHO STEP INSIDE UR GUESS SHOP N BRIWSE WITHOUT BUYING. AND SHE THOUGH I COULI AFFORD TO ISNT????? TO BAD I DIDN'T HAVE HER NAME.. SHE IS SO SUPER SARCASTIC SALESGIRL.
Even though the clothes may be cheap, still there must be some standard in service... Both service and atttitude of the staffs are subpar. This would very much explain what kind of company this is.
Sales is awesome but thats all I could think of. Staff is in their own world
